
1. Use the Oleksii package class to get valid file information ( 
    
    $top = new Core\Reader\File_rider ( file_path, number_of_lines_to_read); 
    
    );

2. Use package class to read csv files (

    use League\Csv\Reader;

    $csv = Reader::createFromPath( __DIR__."/".$top->patch()."/".$top->create_dataname()[0], 'r');

)

3. Use the class to transfer an array of domains to the template controller (

    Core\Reader\Master_views::go_to('Views_controller', [
        "top" => $top->top_list($csv->getContent())
    ]);

)